document_data.History:
''Circa'' [[1486 DR]], Zern was in [[Elventree]], where he possibly hired some adventurers to help [[Elanil Elassidil]] with some [[drow]] arriving on the surface.

Zern was possibly involved in the case of [[dracolich]]es and [[ghost ship]]s wandering the [[Moonsea]] in the {{YearlinkName|1489}}. He said that the Order believed that [[fiend]]ish forces were involved.{{Cite adventurers league/Shadows over the Moonsea|10}}

In the {{YearlinkName|1491}}, he resurfaced in [[Mulmaster]], where he asked adventurers to investigate [[silkroot]], which had recently arrived in the streets of that city.{{Cite adventurers league/Breath of the Yellow Rose|7}}

Later, he assisted [[Lana]] of the [[Monastery of the Yellow Rose]] at the Mulmaster's temple of [[Ilmater]]. He was with her when she informed an adventuring party, who had previously been hired to investigate a strange storm, about the suspect situation at the monastery.
